Package: sammyR
Title: Analysis of Sequential Analysis of MacroMolecules accessibilitY
    sequencing (SAMMY-seq) Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Margherita", "Mutarelli", , "margherita.mutarelli@cnr.it", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to analyse Sequential Analysis of
    MacroMolecules accessibilitY sequencing (SAMMY-seq) data, including
    (a) chromatin compartmentalization analysis to identify A/B
    compartments across chromosomes via CALDER2 and (b) identification of
    differentially enriched solubility regions as described in Wang et
    al. (2025).
